Surgery Digestive System Ureter

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include these codes as defined in http://www.ama-assn.org/go/cpt
    Code Display
    50978 Ureteral endoscopy through ureterotomy, with or without irrigation, instillation, or ureteropyelography, exclusive of radiologic service; with insertion of radioactive substance, with or without biopsy and/or fulguration (not including provision of material)
    51715 Endoscopic injection of implant material into the submucosal tissues of the urethra and/or bladder neck
    53855 Insertion of a temporary prostatic urethral stent, including urethral measurement
